\f1\ldblquote A victory. What kind of a victory? Is that what satisfies you in life? To get to know enough to be a quarter of a Registered Electronician by the time you\rquote re sixty-five?\rdblquote\f0\par
\f1\ldblquote Perhaps by the time I\rquote mthirty-five.\rdblquote\f0\par
\f1\ldblquote And then who\rquote ll want you? Who\rquote ll use you? Where will you go?\rdblquote\f0\par
