\f1\ldblquote And that satisfies you? Tell me! You\rquote ve dragged me to class. You\rquote ve got me to reading and memorizing, too. For what! There\rquote s nothing in it that satisfies me.\rdblquote\f0\par
\f1\ldblquote What good will it do you to deny yourself satisfaction?\rdblquote\f0\par
\f1\ldblquote It means I\rquote ll quit the whole farce. I\rquote ll do as I planned to do in the beginning before you dovey-lovied me out of it. I\rquote m going to force them to\emdash to-\emdash --\emdash\emdash\emdash\rquote\rquote\f0\par
